headline: Latest News In Energy Transition - Nimbus Wind Farm Powers Sustainable Energy Future
summary: Scout Clean Energy recently held a blade signing ceremony to celebrate the progress of the Nimbus Wind Farm project in Green Forest, Arkansas. This event marked a significant milestone in the development of the 180 MW wind farm, which has been in preparation since 2016. As construction advances with an anticipated completion early next year, the project promises to generate sufficient electricity to power over 40,000 homes annually.
